{"tid":2290104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基辛格：美國下任總統應與中國對話管控分歧","createTime":"2020-11-17T18:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T17:56:29.000Z","uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2c2ac5fa0368ec7d79bf869558b1f14059d34da0","tid":2290104,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:45:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560346-20201117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560346-20201117.htm&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1fsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=5eaa72b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560346-20201117.htm&h=d6c8ec74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560346-20201117.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國前國務卿基辛格認為，美國下任總統要與中國對話，通過溝通管控分歧、促成合作。<br />\n<br />\n97歲的基辛格以視像方式出席2020創新經濟論壇，再談中美關係。被問到美國下任總統應如何處理兩國關係時，他認為，美方首先要和中國領導人對話，建立機制保持聯繫，討論需要避免出現的問題。在此之後，雙方溝通的重點可以轉向那些應該實現的問題。中美必須避免雙方的分歧演變成衝突，並且希望能夠促成一些合作。<br />\n<br />\n基辛格說，對中美雙方而言，重要的是理解對方關切所在。雙方必須了解對方的基本觀點、原則以及對國家利益的定義，這樣才能順利開展對話。"},{"pid":"3731732d1c3c17b083e1c982b6793e0c9f24e34d","tid":2290104,"uid":270730,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:47:10.000Z","msg":"含撚啦死基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4811af0236e5a1d06fe3a57bfcee02172fc11e3","tid":2290104,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e54db143bc74734591f6a43d1dc264fbd7579c","tid":2290104,"uid":342855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T21:34:06.000Z","msg":"佢仲未死？"},{"pid":"c5b5eb878e1f82686486830b87faeb0252a99596","tid":2290104,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"